Version 1.3.15 [2026/02/17]
---------------------------
* defined CRC16_MODBUS.
* added StringToBool functionality.
* added StringWithSeparatorToXArray functionalities.
* improvements on Debug and Log.
* debug RTT for ARM environment.
* added colors on debug - where supported.
* added CO2 unit measure.
* added MD HMAC to Crypto layer.
* first support for IAR compiler.
* added FileX layer.
* added isPrint to String layer.
* added StringWithSeparator to String layer.
* added TOMMROC_UTIL_DESIGNATED_SECTION stuff.
* added MemCopySafe and MemMoveSafe.

