Version 1.3.12 [2024/12/02]
---------------------------
* crypto Base64 added.
* generic file system definition added.
* log layer added.
* SQL layer added.
* improvements on DateTime.
* ESP32 RISCV environment added.
* improvements on FS (littlefs) performances.
* some support to uint64_t/int64_t added.
* OsIsFromISR functionality added.
* OsCritical added specificData parameter to be compatible with all the environments.

+ libs
------
    * jsmn REL master (2021/10/14).
    * libhelixmp3 REL master (2019/08/31)
    * littleFs REL 2.9.3 (2024/04/29)
