* added "TOMMROC_DEBUG_PRINTLN_PLUS_STRING_LEN" and "TOMMROC_DEBUG_PRINTLN_PLUS_FLOAT" in Debug layer.
* added RAW type in Debug layer.
* added "IS_PRINT_PENDING" and "IS_SAVE_PENDING" functionality in Debug layer.
* added "WaitForFreeAndPush", "WaitForFreeMultiPush" and "Skip" functionality in FIFO layer.
* added vector module functionality in Geometry layer.
* added JSON builder layer.
* added Sqrt in Math layer.
* added HARD_CLOCK (CPU cycle counter) functionality in Os layer.
* added some unit of measure in UnitMeasure layer.
* for GNUC compiler, added GNUC Major/Minor/Patch version in Version layer.

